{"tid":290974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一年嘅時候送過啲咩禮物","createTime":"2017-06-20T07:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T09:49:22.000Z","uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15918a21b35f95440648a0b47008ea1d7b2e7844","tid":290974,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"整過爆炸盒 蛋糕 送過手錶 銀包 皮帶 cardholder DIY都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔鍾意打機 淨係玩傳說對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有送過最近好hit個隻可以連手機玩傳說打機個隻飛智(?)係咪呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家已經唔知送啲咩 一年之後過兩個月係佢生日 我本身係啲好冇創意嘅人 但係可以好有心思 可唔可以比啲提議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者分享下你地整過或者收過啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4851308d4a897d1d1ac18d1fdc05b578a5bd37","tid":290974,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fe53cf83ab9c3aa52a692ea25032d1ed9f5a06","tid":290974,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:08:42.000Z","msg":"利申絲"},{"pid":"fd41dd52fdc828ff478639ce06dddf3b76010aff","tid":290974,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"腿張開"},{"pid":"0d9222d80f091c04a32378ebdea7915116424aa6","tid":290974,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"處"},{"pid":"996cd6266061ec68ab40e08a2536fc2e10e8312f","tid":290974,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇第啲"},{"pid":"a6a5cec22fb099546f36d0748a575bde82a148cb","tid":290974,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:11:53.000